---
title: Mexican-Style Beef Bake with Cheesy Kumara Topping
description: This delicious beef bake is both warming and full of nutrients - not that you'd know that to look at it. Undercover veg and an irresistible roasted kumara top make this pie the ultimate in comforting food.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ba1d63d30006c583e33a3a2-b91c5b30.jpg
